(700, 68, 'columns_content_0_column_0_content', '<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-66\" src=\"http://honeydigital.co.uk//perrigo-ireland/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/paracetamol.png\" alt=\"paracetamol\" width=\"455\" height=\"375\" />\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Perrigo Paracetamol 500mg Film-Coated Tablets</h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">For the relief of headaches, including migraine and tension headaches, toothache, backache, rheumatic and muscle pains, neuralgia and period pain.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">It also relieves sore throat and the feverishness, aches and pains of colds and flu. The active ingredient is paracetamol which is a painkiller and reduces your temperature when you have a fever.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Perrigo Paracetamol 500mg Film-coated tablets contain Paracetamol. For the treatment of mild to moderate pain. Always read the leaflet.</p>'),
