(1186, 98, 'columns_content_0_column_0_content', '<img class=\"size-full wp-image-66 alignleft\" src=\"http://honeydigital.co.uk//perrigo-ireland/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/paracetamol.png\" alt=\"paracetamol\" width=\"455\" height=\"375\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Headache</li>\r\n 	<li>Toothache</li>\r\n 	<li>Cold &amp; Flu</li>\r\n 	<li>Muscular Pain</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\">Perrigo Paracetamol\r\n500mg Film-Coated Tablets</h3>\r\nThis medicine is used for relief of headaches, including migraine and tension headaches, toothache, backache, rheumatic and muscle pains, neuralgia and period pain.\r\n\r\nIt also relieves feverishness, aches and pains of colds and flu. The active ingredient is paracetamol which is a painkiller and reduces your temperature when you have a fever.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class=\"disclaimer\">Paracetamol 500mg Film-coated Tablets contain Paracetamol.\r\nFor pain relief. Always read the leaflet.</p>'),
